{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"@halkeye/gatsby-source-goodreads","description":"Get the public books from a shelf in Goodreads for use in Gatsby.","keywords":["goodreads","gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"halkeye","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/6d2fc509afca25e1489e65b37214c7cc"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/halkeye/gatsby-source-goodreads"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-goodreads\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-goodreads\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-goodreads</h1>\n<p>Source plugin for pulling your read books into Gatsby from Goodreads API.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-source-goodreads\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        developerKey<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"IAmDeveloperKey\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        goodReadsUserId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"IAmGoodreadsUserId\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        userShelf<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"to-read\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//optional</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"plugin-options\"><a href=\"#plugin-options\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugin options</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>developerKey</strong>: Use your <a href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/api/keys\">Goodreads developer API key</a></li>\n<li><strong>goodReadsUserId</strong>: The Goodreads user ID of the user to get data for.</li>\n<li><strong>userShelf</strong>: <em>OPTIONAL</em>. read, currently-reading, to-read, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query-your-goodread-data-using-graphql\"><a href=\"#how-to-query-your-goodread-data-using-graphql\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query your Goodread data using GraphQL</h2>\n<p>Below is a sample query for fetching the shelfâ€™s books. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> goodRead <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allGoodreadsShelf<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">shelfNames</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"currently-reading\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        shelfNames\n        review <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          reviewID\n          rating\n          votes\n          spoilerFlag\n          dateAdded\n          dateUpdated\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        book <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          bookID\n          isbn\n          isbn13\n          textReviewsCount\n          uri\n          link\n          title\n          titleWithoutSeries\n          imageUrl\n          smallImageUrl\n          largeImageUrl\n          description\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/@halkeye/gatsby-source-goodreads/","id":"3b81b489-9671-5a55-b325-aa521600ca7a"}}